My point is this is what natural selection will predict,

44:34.340 --> 44:36.340
that there should be multiple different types of eye

44:36.340 --> 44:39.340
in different environments, different ecological contexts,

44:39.340 --> 44:43.340
different types of eye with different functioning.

44:43.340 --> 44:45.340
We don't see the evolutionary intermediates,

44:45.340 --> 44:48.340
but we see ecologically all the different types.

44:48.340 --> 44:51.340
We would expect to see something similar in bacteria.

44:51.340 --> 44:53.340
We would expect to see some bacteria that have something

44:53.340 --> 44:55.340
that's a bit like a nucleus,

44:55.340 --> 44:57.340
or some that do something a bit like sex,

